{"tid":2249192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港故事落幕 萬人記真相  閉館前最後抗爭 光時口號遍展廳","createTime":"2020-10-19T07:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T07:38:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fa5ece3eafb4971ce802fbeba57050b5da657681","tid":2249192,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:31:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/CAFSYQF4DJFSJJ6ZNLZAV4CFMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FCAFSYQF4DJFSJJ6ZNLZAV4CFMQ%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Ziukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=57c2257a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FCAFSYQF4DJFSJJ6ZNLZAV4CFMQ%2F&h=8f536a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/CAFSYQF4DJFSJJ6ZNLZAV4CFMQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n香港故事落幕 萬人記真相 <br />\n閉館前最後抗爭 光時口號遍展廳<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港故事變樣之前，港人用眼睛紀錄歷史。香港歷史博物館開放19年的常設展覽《香港故事》，今日起關閉兩年進行翻新工程。近萬人趁最後一日前來參觀，其中「香港回歸」展區最受歡迎，有市民憂慮翻新後的歷史面目全非，盼用記憶及相片傳承歷史。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：新展覽不提武肺 反修例<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PvokoJF6Dv_JMcnJ7sQyPPAb31I=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WQXT77GB2RH6FMJVTMKXKXHSMI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPvokoJF6Dv_JMcnJ7sQyPPAb31I%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWQXT77GB2RH6FMJVTMKXKXHSMI.jpg&h=65f1bae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■展館內掛有前國家主席江澤民贈港「香港明天更好」題字照片，不少人舉「光復」留影。何量鈞攝<br />\n<br />\n昨《香港故事》展覽最後一日，不少人把握機會參觀。館內最人頭湧湧的地點非「香港回歸」展區莫屬，當中尤以港英時期香港總督旗成為熱點，不少人爭相與旗幟合影。有參觀巿民於《中英聯合聲明》及後記的展板上，放置「SAVE 12 HK YOUTH」的紙張，或貼上「光復香港 時代革命」的標語貼紙。<br />\n<br />\n由前國家主席江澤民向香港送贈「香港明天更好」題字的照片，同樣成為市民的「打卡」熱點。有人在相片旁舉起「光復」二字，亦有人舉起「五大訴求、缺一不可」的手勢。臨近閉館前，更有市民突然在「香港回歸」展覽廳高叫反修例口號，作閉館前的最後抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/P4kndKvOc3D_Wr21VoIH6GeDStk=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JYNN63EGF5BLVJFE7IDFI4FVEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FP4kndKvOc3D_Wr21VoIH6GeDStk%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJYNN63EGF5BLVJFE7IDFI4FVEM.jpg&h=eeddd323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■香港歷史博物館常設展覽「香港故事」昨最後一日，大批市民排隊入場參觀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8Y_qGh50xq8uEB7zDUHNiEVomgI=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q4K6CEDDNJBO3M2PDEN5RU3S5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8Y_qGh50xq8uEB7zDUHNiEVomgI%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ4K6CEDDNJBO3M2PDEN5RU3S5E.jpg&h=9c388733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有身穿港英標誌衣服的參觀者，細看館內港督展品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_TI3JceXO8nRvdl8b_qeuRp2h70=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UB4YU7DY5JG3FOPSHEDTBY4XIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_TI3JceXO8nRvdl8b_qeuRp2h70%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUB4YU7DY5JG3FOPSHEDTBY4XIE.jpg&h=90f48824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港英時期展品或在兩年後的新展覽中消失。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英殖時期展品恐難再現<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。，「應該就唔會再有以前英殖嘅嘢可以睇，國旗呀嗰啲，應該唔會有機會再見到」。他坦言館方在這個敏感時刻翻新展覽，難免令人感到奇怪，「大家都知呢幾年發生乜事，加上歷史係由勝利者去寫，所以惟有用我哋所記得嘅記憶再話畀下一代知」。<br />\n<br />\n許同學與楊同學亦坐上展覽的尾班車 ，「見證吓香港歷史未俾人改嘅一面」。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n。<br />\n「由細個睇到𠵱家，都會擔心咁啲文物會去邊呢」。她同樣懷疑翻新展覽屬政治任務，新展覽必定「會無咗啲嘢」，「殖民地色彩重要嘅嘢呀、政權交換上都有機會被換咗，內容上唔知會唔會更改喇」。<br />\n<br />\n康文署指會參考諮詢結果翻新展覽，當中建議刪除自然歷史部份，以及將內容延伸至97年後，並設立專題展區。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n歷史博物館指昨有逾9,800人次入場，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。，「我哋以前可能見過，但生活上冇諗過。我哋生活過程可能覺得有乜咁特別啫，但過咗一段時間，我哋先會睇到佢嘅影響、重要。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LtSYwq6PLhk1sdaMsFGqL6X5oZU=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IMM6EQDAJJERJAHXX7OMXJR37E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLtSYwq6PLhk1sdaMsFGqL6X5oZU%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIMM6EQDAJJERJAHXX7OMXJR37E.jpg&h=c52a4786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■近百人在「香港故事」展館外拍攝閉幕一刻及拍手歡呼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1DlWzWPzAE0dZ48tstIc_upePX4=/1465x684/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T4MUBGYTFZCU5EF6SKPV54LSFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1DlWzWPzAE0dZ48tstIc_upePX4%3D%2F1465x684%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT4MUBGYTFZCU5EF6SKPV54LSFM.jpg&h=b4b0ab53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff992dfc5a061c04dea86869f102ae52144c211b","tid":2249192,"uid":42526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/CAFSYQF4DJFSJJ6ZNLZAV4CFMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FCAFSYQF4DJFSJJ6ZNLZAV4CFMQ%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Ziukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=57c2257a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FCAFSYQF4DJFSJJ6ZNLZAV4CFMQ%2F&h=8f536a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/CAFSYQF4DJFSJJ6ZNLZAV4CFMQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8Y_qGh50xq8uEB7zDUHNiEVomgI=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q4K6CEDDNJBO3M2PDEN5RU3S5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8Y_qGh50xq8uEB7zDUHNiEVomgI%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ4K6CEDDNJBO3M2PDEN5RU3S5E.jpg&h=9c388733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有身穿港英標誌衣服的參觀者，細看館內港督展品。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢件衫好似幾靚"},{"pid":"0bd0ccd437edc7f8f7fdcef1982e120b92c17133","tid":2249192,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80063dd0d8143a11305686a763c67ebc48c72624","tid":2249192,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"遲下變成明日大愚博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n共鏟主意博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n習林炒飯紀念館<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}